ael-stipe-sinead-oconnor-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/michael-stipe-sinead-oconnor-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/michael-stipe-sinead-oconnor-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/michael-stipe-sinead-oconnor-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/michael-stipe-sinead-oconnor-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/r-e-m">REM</a>主唱迈克尔·斯蒂普<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">(Michael Stipe)</a>重新翻唱了西妮德·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor)</a>的《我们相识的最后一天》，向这位已故明星致敬。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位广受赞誉的爱尔兰歌手和活动家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">于本周（7 月 26 日）去世，享年 56 岁</a>，她的家人宣布。据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-was-found-unresponsive-at-home-police-say-3474196">她被发现在伦敦的家中失去知觉</a>，她的死亡并未被视为可疑。</p><p>斯蒂普在 Instagram 上发布了两人的照片向奥康纳致敬，并表示他“无言以对”来描述这一消息，之后，斯蒂普向歌迷们推荐了他在 1996 年表演的《The Last Day Of Our Acquainance》的翻唱版本。</p><p>请参阅下面的封面和致敬。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvOoK6Aurg7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14p