“再多的麻烦也无法掩盖她的才华；奥康纳是一位罕见的艺术家，她决心利用自己的平台进行善行，人们会记住她，不仅因为她声音的美丽，还因为她声音的力量。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-stipe-revisits-cover-of-the-last-day-of-our-acquaintance-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474570">迈克尔·斯蒂普 (Michael Stipe) 重温《我们相识的最后一天》封面向西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 致敬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Lathums 将在 Kendal Calling 演出秘密演出，然后立即发行黑胶唱片https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lathums-to-play-secret-set-at-kendal-calling-and-then-immediately-release-it-on-vinyl-3474556?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-lathums-to-play-secret-set-at-kendal-calling-and-then-remediately-release-it-on-vinylWill Richards Fri, 28 Jul 2023 07:30:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3474556 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莱瑟姆一家，亚历克斯·摩尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>限量版唱片将在音乐节和网上发售</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lathums-to-play-secret-set-at-kendal-calling-and-then-immediately-release-it-on-vinyl-3474556">The Lathums 在 Kendal Calling 秘密演出并立即以黑胶唱片形式发行的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莱瑟姆一家，亚历克斯·摩尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2022_thelathums_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lathums">Lathums</a>将于今天（7 月 28 日）在 Kendal Calling 进行秘密演出，然后立即以黑胶唱片形式发行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-lathums-interview-2023-from-nothing-to-a-little-bit-more-wigan-brandon-flowers-3395597">：Lathums：“我们将一起接管世界——我们必须尽可能紧密地联系在一起”</a></strong></li></ul><p>维冈乐队将在音乐节上演奏<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-burgess">Tim Burgess</a>的 Tim Peaks 舞台，然后立即 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-vinyl-pressing-plant-to-open-in-middlesbrough-3135337">在米德尔斯堡的 Press On Vinyl</a>进行混音、母带处理并剪辑成黑胶唱片。</p><p>黑胶唱片将发售 200 张，其中 100 张将于当天下午 4 点返回 Kendal Calling 出售，其他则<a href="https://pressonvinyl.com/">在此处在线销售</a>。</p><p>在线销售的所有收益将捐给<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lathums-launch-chance-to-see-charity-fund-for-children-and-young-people-3414040">The Lathums 自己的慈善机构 Chance To See</a> ，而第 1/200 号将进行抽奖，收益将捐给 Burgess 的助学金计划 Help Us Help Bands。</p><p> Burgess 向<em>NME</em>讲述了此次活动：“让 The Lathums 重返 Tim Peaks 真是太棒了——2019 年的 Kendal Calling 是他们参加的第一个音乐节，这一次他们将拥有两张排名第一的专辑。 ” </p><figure id="attachment_3474563" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474563" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474563" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl.jpeg" alt="莱瑟姆一家" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lathums-tim-peaks-vinyl-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474563" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：出版社。</figcaption></figure><p> Lathums 今年早些时候发起了 Chance To See，该慈善机构帮助为年轻人在家乡维冈提供创意机会。</p><p>作为与文化教育慈善机构 Curious Minds 长期合作伙伴关系的一部分，这项慈善事业将 100% 的资金直接用于维冈的成熟青年和社区提供者，特别是帮助面临经济或社会不平等的年轻人。</p><p>乐队在一份声明中表示：“在困难时期拥有一把原声吉他就意味着 The Lathums 成为可能，并让我们能够逃离当时生活中发生的一切。”</p><p> “有些人无法接触到吉他或遇到任何其他形式的创造力，而永远没有这样的机会的想法让我们心碎。当人们的注意力集中在寒冷月份的供暖和饮食上时，通过与 Curious Minds 共同启动这一基金，我们还希望关注一些其他让生活变得有价值的事情。”</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lathums-land-second-number-one-album-with-from-nothing-to-a-little-bit-more-3411568">The Lathums 凭借新唱片《From Nothing To A Little Bit More》第二次登上英国冠军宝座</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lathums-to-play-secret-set-at-kendal-calling-and-then-immediately-release-it-on-vinyl-3474556">The Lathums 在 Kendal Calling 秘密演出并立即以黑胶唱片形式发行的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
